"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=site:foreignaffairs.com","A Hidden Force in the Middle East: How Arab Public Opinion Constrains Normalization With Israel","https://www.foreignaffairs.com/israel/hidden-force-middle-east","Thu, 12 Jun 2025 04:00:00 GMT","

