"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=site:entertainmentnow.com","HGTV's Tarek El Moussa & Christina Haack Celebrate Daughter's Big Milestone","https://entertainmentnow.com/hgtv/tarek-el-moussa-christina-haack-daughter/","Thu, 12 Jun 2025 15:47:43 GMT","

Tarek El Moussa and Christina Haack‘s daughter Taylor just reached a big milestone, and the HGTV stars took to Instagram to celebrate it. El Moussa and Haack shared that they're proud and excited for their daughter as she embarks on her next chapter.

A post shared by Heather Rae El Moussa (@theheatherraeelmoussa)

On June 10, Haack took to Instagram to shared a photo of herself with El Moussa, their kids Taylor and Brayden, and Heather Rae El Moussa. She also posted a photo on her Instagram Stories that noted, “Beautiful 8th grade grad.”

“Taylor we are so proud of you and so excited for you to head into the next stage of your life,” she wrote in the caption.

Haack continued, “Our beautiful, smart, incredible, bright light we all love and adore you. We hope all the mistakes you've watched us make throughout your life help to guide you to a brighter future … 😜🤣🤣 love you baby.”

She added, “High school here we come!!!”

Both Tarek and Heather Rae reposted Haack's post on their Instagram accounts.

In another post on her Instagram Stories, Haack and her ex-husband posed with Taylor. She noted, “We've been through a lot, but one thing we've always been is great co-parents.”

A post shared by Tarek El Moussa (@therealtarekelmoussa)

Fans lit up Haack's post with messages congratulating Taylor. Many fans also pointed out how the blended family gets along so well.

“Love how your family works TOGETHER!! Huge props for maturity and KIDS FIRST,” one person commented.

Another fan remarked, “Woo hoo!! Congrats 👏 P.S. I love that mom and step-mom are together and dad is on the other side 😂🫶”

“Parents are never perfect but to have kids love us through the battles is absolute perfection 💕 It's a realization when kids understand their parents are human too and they love them more for that!” one of Haack's followers shared. “Love your blended families! Congrats to Taylor! 👏 The next fun chapter begins for you!”

Other fans noted, “What an amazing photo of gorgeous folks, and what a great example of a blended FAMILY” and “What a wonderful family. It makes me feel so happy seeing how all of you are getting along.”

Some people shared notes for Taylor, including, “From the little girl we've seen on TV to a grown girl off to high school — All the best Taylor” and “Beautiful!!! Congratulations Taylor!! Best of luck in high school.”

